    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国海警加剧南海紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名官员表示，菲律宾周三指责中国海警使用高压水枪损坏了其两艘船只，从而加剧了南海的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:40:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾对中国就职后的演习保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高安全官员周三表示，在当选总统赖清德本月就职后，台湾对中国进行军事演习保持警惕，并指出北京通常在六月开始此类演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于芯片需求增长，韩国出口连续第七个月增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-exports-rise-seventh-month-growing-chip-demand-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三贸易数据显示，韩国 4 月份出口连续第七个月增长，因对芯片的强劲需求继续引领增长，同时汽车销量和美国出货量攀升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-exports-rise-seventh-month-growing-chip-demand-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
